{"tid":2508172,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"阿斯利康和BioNTech正研混合使用 國藥及科興表示也有興趣","createTime":"2021-04-28T14:06:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T14:20:21.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d2e6ce9a31667379c7e568cfaef654928cb7c228","tid":2508172,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T14:06:07.000Z","msg":"國藥及科興考慮混合其他新冠疫苗接種 提升保護力<br />\n<br />\n內地國藥及科興藥廠，正考慮混合其他藥廠疫苗注射方式，加強預防新冠病毒。目前有兩款新冠滅活疫苗的國藥，旗下中國生物技術公司的國際合作部負責人李萌在一場國際會議上透露，未來有「序貫免疫」使用計劃。科興就說，正與中國疾控中心在內的人員初步討論，將科興疫苗與其他疫苗混合使用。專家指，「序貫免疫」即混合不同疫苗，以提高治療效果，藥廠正尋找最佳時機和組合。<br />\n<br />\n英國亦有科學家正研究將阿斯利康和BioNTech，兩款不同技術的疫苗混合注射，現時正測試相隔多長時間接種。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2389316\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2389316&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzYZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=f4c545f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2389316</a>"},{"pid":"afb5c10e92ab00afde54535d0ee24309256eb686","tid":2508172,"uid":137038,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T14:07:46.000Z","msg":"睇標題都覺得尷尬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58c46453f05484974e9d29e68467590a321a1cbe","tid":2508172,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T14:08:40.000Z","msg":"全球人體實驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8102fec876d9be8f12e9405080c7479f179692","tid":2508172,"uid":7369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T14:08:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmah3NSj868xj7Hj7JAVcAAj9f1DgoxzfMAydXAnDcj3Si?filename=TFdMtLQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTFdMtLQ.png&h=63ec9300&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"61781b99d52fa09571d921e58695dbcab51d7e9d","tid":2508172,"uid":78968,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T14:15:17.000Z"